'''Indonesia''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in March 2019. Its default cities are the capital, Jakarta, along with Bali.

Indonesia was part of a March 2019 [[Updates|update]] that added 8 new countries into the game. The other 7 were [[Portugal]], [[Norway]], [[Singapore]], [[Denmark]], [[Finland]], [[Estonia]], and [[Romania]]. This update was also the update that brought [[Pets]] for the first time. This update was also the first to have multiple new countries being added other than the ones originally released.

Indonesia is along with [[Iran]], [[Saudi Arabia]] and [[Singapore]] that [[Crime|Drug trafficking and drug possession]] is punished by death penalty.

